WEBVTT

00:00:10.600 --> 00:00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

00:01:06.540 --> 00:01:07.220
[The Eternal Fragrance]

00:01:07.220 --> 00:01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

00:01:12.020 --> 00:01:15.140
[Episode 24]

00:01:16.830 --> 00:01:19.010
Master is at Hushe Peak.

00:01:20.830 --> 00:01:22.140
Jiaping's distant-sensing talisman?

00:01:24.080 --> 00:01:25.090
He's in danger.

00:01:25.640 --> 00:01:26.290
Jiaping?

00:01:27.750 --> 00:01:28.580
Have you found him?

00:01:32.640 --> 00:01:33.530
Where is Hushe?

00:01:34.110 --> 00:01:34.810
What happened?

00:01:36.240 --> 00:01:38.620
It's Hushe Peak, the secret forbidden area of Wuyue Court.

00:01:41.910 --> 00:01:42.780
I'll go back with you.

00:02:01.390 --> 00:02:01.980
My Lord.

00:02:05.030 --> 00:02:05.780
Rakshasa.

00:02:11.030 --> 00:02:12.970
You finally remember me, My Lord.

00:02:17.320 --> 00:02:19.090
You slew Zong Quan

00:02:19.590 --> 00:02:21.250
And rid the demon clan of Longming Sanctuary.

00:02:21.900 --> 00:02:23.780
Truly a joyous victory!

00:02:26.990 --> 00:02:28.340
Through the chaos in the Yue State,

00:02:29.800 --> 00:02:32.570
You've seen clearly

00:02:32.590 --> 00:02:34.650
The shameless faces of all immortal sects.

00:02:39.040 --> 00:02:41.940
What's the difference between the immortal sects or the demon clan?

00:02:43.110 --> 00:02:45.690
All schemes for petty self-interest.

00:02:46.670 --> 00:02:49.650
I ordered you to return. Why didn't you?

00:02:51.480 --> 00:02:54.570
Five centuries ago, we crossed the East Sea.

00:02:54.900 --> 00:02:56.410
You said back then

00:02:56.870 --> 00:02:59.060
This would be our new home.

00:03:00.240 --> 00:03:01.060
Have you forgotten?

00:03:04.320 --> 00:03:05.780
Now I'm reborn as a mortal.

00:03:06.550 --> 00:03:09.250
All the past means nothing to me.

00:03:10.150 --> 00:03:11.370
I came to you for another matter.

00:03:12.240 --> 00:03:15.180
Lifei and I are going to Hushe Peak.

00:03:16.620 --> 00:03:17.740
Jiang Lifei again.

00:03:18.320 --> 00:03:19.970
She is merely an ordinary woman.

00:03:20.270 --> 00:03:21.620
You are the great Demon Lord.

00:03:21.760 --> 00:03:23.370
Would you abandon your grand cause

00:03:23.390 --> 00:03:24.250
And sink low for her?

00:03:24.480 --> 00:03:26.250
You keep addressing me as My Lord,

00:03:26.320 --> 00:03:27.650
Yet you act on your own

00:03:28.430 --> 00:03:30.060
And question every choice I make.

00:03:32.620 --> 00:03:36.220
Do you expect me to obey you instead?

00:03:46.430 --> 00:03:48.300
I... I dare not.

00:04:05.830 --> 00:04:07.340
You came back, after all.

00:04:12.360 --> 00:04:15.810
Master, I wish to borrow the Hexagonal Prism.

00:04:17.080 --> 00:04:20.180
I fear once you uncover the truth you seek,

00:04:20.790 --> 00:04:24.570
You'll sink into mire with no escape.

00:04:26.760 --> 00:04:27.450
My senior brother

00:04:29.560 --> 00:04:31.810
And the old man who raised me

00:04:34.120 --> 00:04:35.420
Must be waiting for me.

00:04:58.350 --> 00:05:03.570
Lifei, we shall be master and disciple for all time.

00:05:06.390 --> 00:05:10.100
Zhuiyu Peak will always be your home.

00:05:19.580 --> 00:05:20.100
Go.

00:05:22.600 --> 00:05:27.000
♪With you, we climb bleak cliffs beneath endless gloom♪

00:05:27.290 --> 00:05:29.440
♪Bow our heads and endure bitter gales♪

00:05:29.610 --> 00:05:35.240
♪Ambition surges; we hold new feasts amid thorns♪

00:05:35.320 --> 00:05:39.360
♪Let frost, snow and rain block the long stone steps♪

00:05:39.480 --> 00:05:41.680
♪I tread fleeting mist beneath my feet♪

00:05:41.800 --> 00:05:47.480
♪At last I see, life's end lies boundless wild free♪

00:05:47.800 --> 00:05:58.880
♪Don't idle away time. We shall meet atop the peak♪

00:06:05.980 --> 00:06:07.620
Yangling, that's the direction of Wengu Hall.

00:06:07.980 --> 00:06:09.420
It's demonic energy! Go.

00:06:33.270 --> 00:06:34.370
Why is the maple forest stretching further?

00:06:36.520 --> 00:06:38.810
You're too hasty and fell for an illusion.

00:07:17.880 --> 00:07:18.860
Are we at home?

00:07:25.320 --> 00:07:27.980
No, we're still on Hushe Peak.

00:07:45.440 --> 00:07:46.060
Watch out!

00:08:03.230 --> 00:08:04.130
Where are we?

00:08:06.390 --> 00:08:08.810
I've heard that when immortal cultivators reach a certain realm,

00:08:09.390 --> 00:08:10.180
They can open

00:08:10.200 --> 00:08:11.450
A private world of their own,

00:08:12.200 --> 00:08:14.370
Complete with mountains, rivers, sun, moon, and boundless clouds.

00:08:15.590 --> 00:08:16.770
They set all the laws

00:08:17.150 --> 00:08:18.570
Governing this realm,

00:08:19.230 --> 00:08:22.010
Which is known as a miniature realm.

00:08:23.560 --> 00:08:24.010
Whose

00:08:24.680 --> 00:08:26.210
Miniature realm is this?

00:08:33.830 --> 00:08:34.890
It's Cuihua Peak's restriction spell.

00:08:36.750 --> 00:08:39.660
This must be Cuixuan's miniature realm.

00:08:41.960 --> 00:08:43.180
Where's the Hexagonal Prism?

00:08:54.080 --> 00:08:54.570
Go.

00:09:06.800 --> 00:09:08.690
Didn't expect Cuixuan's miniature realm

00:09:09.400 --> 00:09:11.060
To have such thick spirit energy.

00:09:12.160 --> 00:09:13.850
Is this Hushe Peak's secret?

00:09:19.040 --> 00:09:19.690
What's up?

00:09:22.230 --> 00:09:23.610
I sensed weird energy all around.

00:09:24.990 --> 00:09:28.180
Feels like demonic energy, but not quite.

00:09:29.320 --> 00:09:31.850
Why would demonic energy exist in an immortal secret land?

00:10:00.510 --> 00:10:01.900
Flowers growing out of skeletons.

00:10:02.350 --> 00:10:05.380
They live off demonic energy

00:10:05.400 --> 00:10:06.090
And vengeful spirits.

00:10:06.960 --> 00:10:09.490
The more hatred, the brighter the flowers.

00:10:14.350 --> 00:10:15.210
Their roots trap

00:10:15.920 --> 00:10:17.690
Lost, unwilling souls

00:10:17.870 --> 00:10:19.540
In dirty mud,

00:10:21.440 --> 00:10:24.090
With no escape forever.

00:10:25.990 --> 00:10:26.940
All these demon bones

00:10:27.440 --> 00:10:29.300
Had their power sucked dry when they lived.

00:10:31.040 --> 00:10:32.810
Is this Zong Quan's Spirit-Devouring Art?

00:10:33.320 --> 00:10:37.140
No, it's Wuyue Court's Spirit-Binding Art,

00:10:37.750 --> 00:10:39.850
Same as the binding barrier of Lilie Valley.

00:10:41.800 --> 00:10:45.540
You mean Cuixuan's trained by using demon spirits?

00:10:59.350 --> 00:11:00.330
Human hearts carry dark schemes.

00:11:01.320 --> 00:11:06.060
What's the difference between the immortal sects or the demon clan?

00:11:11.800 --> 00:11:14.610
Calm down. Don't turn into a Yecha.

00:11:17.350 --> 00:11:18.140
I'm fine.

00:11:20.230 --> 00:11:21.260
No aura here.

00:11:22.470 --> 00:11:25.660
No traces of living things are left here. Let's leave.

00:11:26.350 --> 00:11:26.900
Wait.

00:11:29.960 --> 00:11:31.780
There's a faint aura lingering.

00:12:10.160 --> 00:12:10.970
Who are you?

00:12:26.110 --> 00:12:27.690
The spirit energy doesn't work at all, Xiuyuan.

00:12:35.870 --> 00:12:36.730
His heart meridians are severed.

00:12:38.110 --> 00:12:38.940
He won't make it.

00:12:40.440 --> 00:12:41.140
No.

00:12:41.510 --> 00:12:43.140
As long as he is alive, there will be hope.

00:12:58.660 --> 00:12:59.260
Lifei.

00:13:04.800 --> 00:13:05.730
Sir, hold on.

00:13:06.110 --> 00:13:07.140
I'll get you out of here.

00:13:11.080 --> 00:13:11.660
Don't move.

00:13:17.280 --> 00:13:18.090
How could this happen?

00:14:24.560 --> 00:14:25.330
Qingcheng.

00:14:26.560 --> 00:14:27.180
Go.

00:14:33.200 --> 00:14:34.260
Master.

00:14:41.630 --> 00:14:42.490
Master!

00:14:45.800 --> 00:14:46.730
Master!

00:14:46.750 --> 00:14:47.090
Lifei.

00:14:47.110 --> 00:14:48.020
Master!

00:14:48.400 --> 00:14:48.970
Lifei.

00:14:49.710 --> 00:14:50.570
Go.

00:14:51.320 --> 00:14:52.730
- Let's get out of here. - No!

00:14:52.750 --> 00:14:55.570
No! Master!

00:14:55.990 --> 00:14:58.330
Don't leave me!

00:15:01.280 --> 00:15:03.690
Don't abandon me!

00:15:05.470 --> 00:15:08.450
Master! Master!

00:15:11.510 --> 00:15:13.570
Master! Master!

00:15:17.230 --> 00:15:18.380
- Master! - Lifei.

00:15:18.560 --> 00:15:19.180
Master!

00:15:40.110 --> 00:15:41.260
Master!

00:15:42.320 --> 00:15:43.420
Master!

00:15:56.560 --> 00:15:57.610
Qingcheng!

00:16:20.320 --> 00:16:24.210
Foolish brats, how dare you ruin my secret realm!

00:16:24.800 --> 00:16:26.490
So this is indeed your miniature realm.

00:16:28.830 --> 00:16:32.210
It's you! You killed him.

00:16:34.040 --> 00:16:35.780
You killed my master!

00:16:36.560 --> 00:16:37.540
Your master?

00:16:38.080 --> 00:16:39.210
I'll kill you!

00:16:45.680 --> 00:16:46.210
Lifei!

00:16:56.560 --> 00:16:57.490
Demons.

00:16:58.400 --> 00:17:00.570
They're demon spies. Seize them!

00:17:01.750 --> 00:17:04.660
Jiang Lifei, Lei Xiuyuan, you have nowhere to run.

00:17:16.160 --> 00:17:17.290
Dead as you are,

00:17:17.710 --> 00:17:19.690
Your remnants still dare stir trouble.

00:17:20.230 --> 00:17:22.450
Do you think destroying my miniature realm

00:17:22.470 --> 00:17:24.580
And crippling my spirit roots can stop me?

00:17:24.600 --> 00:17:25.660
Listen!

00:17:25.680 --> 00:17:27.420
That girl is your disciple.

00:17:27.920 --> 00:17:31.050
The Senluo Grand Art must be on her.

00:17:31.070 --> 00:17:34.290
Qingcheng, be patient.

00:17:34.790 --> 00:17:36.580
I'll bring her back soon.

00:17:36.840 --> 00:17:37.900
Once I fetch her,

00:17:38.160 --> 00:17:40.900
You can reunite with her.

00:18:47.400 --> 00:18:49.620
Zhaomin, what are you doing here?

00:18:49.990 --> 00:18:50.730
Qin.

00:18:54.990 --> 00:18:56.900
I should be asking you the same.

00:18:57.510 --> 00:18:58.940
This is near Zhuiyu Peak.

00:18:59.340 --> 00:19:00.860
Where did you come from?

00:19:01.070 --> 00:19:02.820
You nearly scared Zhaomin.

00:19:05.310 --> 00:19:06.970
I was ordered to capture demon spies.

00:19:09.340 --> 00:19:10.420
Demon spies?

00:19:11.710 --> 00:19:12.450
Where?

00:19:18.100 --> 00:19:18.860
Where are they?

00:19:20.310 --> 00:19:20.940
She and I?

00:19:21.960 --> 00:19:22.530
No.

00:19:23.230 --> 00:19:24.380
We only planned

00:19:24.400 --> 00:19:26.100
To pick fresh morning herbs together.

00:19:26.270 --> 00:19:28.380
Why call us spies, Yangling?

00:19:28.640 --> 00:19:29.820
What's your deal?

00:19:30.200 --> 00:19:31.820
Who said you're demon spies?

00:19:32.230 --> 00:19:35.010
You just said it, right?

00:19:35.100 --> 00:19:35.860
You heard clearly, huh?

00:19:37.440 --> 00:19:37.970
Yangling,

00:19:38.230 --> 00:19:40.580
Do you think everyone's a spy?

00:19:41.160 --> 00:19:44.490
You even accused Lifei before.

00:19:46.710 --> 00:19:47.290
I know the truth.

00:19:47.880 --> 00:19:49.940
She rejected you,

00:19:49.960 --> 00:19:51.140
So you're jealous of her.

00:19:51.160 --> 00:19:51.690
You!

00:20:05.070 --> 00:20:06.730
Can't believe you struck out!

00:20:07.160 --> 00:20:08.210
Zhaomin, back me up.

00:20:08.710 --> 00:20:10.180
He threw the first punch.

00:20:10.880 --> 00:20:13.140
I won't back down from a fight.

00:20:13.160 --> 00:20:15.340
Come on, let's settle this.

00:20:20.640 --> 00:20:22.180
Don't run. Let's go to Cuixuan...

00:20:22.960 --> 00:20:24.580
Stop pretending. Go check how they are.

00:20:40.600 --> 00:20:42.420
Are you okay? Bad injuries?

00:20:43.200 --> 00:20:45.580
We're fine. Why are you here?

00:20:45.990 --> 00:20:47.970
Master noticed the Hexagonal Prism went haywire

00:20:48.230 --> 00:20:49.290
And sent us to help you.

00:20:56.680 --> 00:20:57.820
Tell him I'm thankful.

00:20:59.160 --> 00:21:01.490
What happened last night could get him into trouble.

00:21:02.310 --> 00:21:04.420
It's fine. He knows how to handle it.

00:21:04.960 --> 00:21:07.140
But look, it's daytime now.

00:21:07.400 --> 00:21:09.210
The whole sect is under strict guard.

00:21:09.680 --> 00:21:10.940
How will you escape?

00:21:13.360 --> 00:21:15.660
Don't worry. I know a hidden path in the mountains.

00:21:15.880 --> 00:21:17.290
You can leave without being noticed.

00:21:17.710 --> 00:21:19.210
No more delays, let's go.

00:21:21.230 --> 00:21:21.770
Watch your step.

00:21:22.400 --> 00:21:23.340
- Stay safe, Lifei. - This way.

00:21:25.120 --> 00:21:25.530
Hurry up.

00:21:28.160 --> 00:21:28.820
That's impossible.

00:21:29.960 --> 00:21:32.290
Xiuyuan is quiet and stubborn,

00:21:32.960 --> 00:21:34.340
But he always respects his masters and behaves properly.

00:21:34.790 --> 00:21:36.900
He's never done anything to betray the sect.

00:21:38.200 --> 00:21:41.100
Cuixuan, you said they're demon spies.

00:21:41.160 --> 00:21:41.940
Got any proof?

00:21:42.550 --> 00:21:45.250
Lei Xiuyuan and Jiang Lifei snuck into the forbidden area at night,

00:21:45.270 --> 00:21:46.250
Releasing demonic energy.

00:21:47.640 --> 00:21:50.860
If they aren't spies, how can they use demonic arts?

00:21:52.200 --> 00:21:55.290
As to what happened at Lilie Valley last time,

00:21:56.880 --> 00:21:58.380
They must be guilty.

00:21:59.230 --> 00:21:59.820
Cuixuan,

00:22:00.510 --> 00:22:02.050
You personally chose

00:22:02.070 --> 00:22:03.580
Those top disciples

00:22:03.680 --> 00:22:04.970
To fix the valley barrier back then.

00:22:07.470 --> 00:22:08.050
Yes.

00:22:09.200 --> 00:22:11.140
They had injuries all over them,

00:22:11.790 --> 00:22:13.690
But you forced them to go.

00:22:13.960 --> 00:22:15.970
I tried talking you out of it, but failed.

00:22:17.270 --> 00:22:19.210
As for the demonic energy on them,

00:22:19.440 --> 00:22:21.860
They probably got tainted

00:22:21.960 --> 00:22:23.730
When fighting demons.

00:22:24.880 --> 00:22:28.050
Cuixuan, what's hidden

00:22:28.790 --> 00:22:30.530
In Hushe Peak's forbidden area?

00:22:30.750 --> 00:22:32.250
Don't you know

00:22:32.400 --> 00:22:34.010
Why I lock Hushe Peak up?

00:22:34.840 --> 00:22:37.900
I know well if someone's

00:22:38.600 --> 00:22:40.450
Tainted or using demonic arts.

00:22:40.840 --> 00:22:41.940
I wouldn't frame them.

00:22:43.270 --> 00:22:44.210
Easy there, Cuixuan.

00:22:44.790 --> 00:22:45.490
Chongyi

00:22:45.510 --> 00:22:47.450
Only wants what's best for Wuyue Court.

00:22:48.070 --> 00:22:50.940
This must be a misunderstanding, I think.

00:22:51.270 --> 00:22:52.140
Misunderstanding?

00:22:52.840 --> 00:22:54.580
Jiang Lifei is always stirring up trouble.

00:22:55.310 --> 00:22:57.900
I bet she dragged Xiuyuan into all this.

00:22:58.510 --> 00:22:59.450
Nonsense!

00:22:59.840 --> 00:23:02.010
Lei Xiuyuan lured her instead!

00:23:02.100 --> 00:23:03.690
I'm still mad thinking about it.

00:23:03.840 --> 00:23:04.820
Last time in Duantu,

00:23:04.920 --> 00:23:06.940
Jiang Lifei was weak,

00:23:06.960 --> 00:23:08.210
And Lei Xiuyuan actually...

00:23:09.600 --> 00:23:10.900
I don't even want to say it out loud.

00:23:15.960 --> 00:23:18.100
Cuixuan, your aura is unstable.

00:23:18.400 --> 00:23:19.770
Looks like your spirit energy backfired on you.

00:23:20.230 --> 00:23:21.340
Did you get hurt?

00:23:23.640 --> 00:23:25.820
Those two spies ambushed me.

00:23:26.160 --> 00:23:28.820
I let my guard slip, but I'm fine.

00:23:29.470 --> 00:23:30.860
Brief meditation is enough.

00:23:31.100 --> 00:23:31.970
It's simply out of line!

00:23:33.680 --> 00:23:35.210
I mean Lifei and Xiuyuan.

00:23:36.600 --> 00:23:38.770
Cuixuan, take care.

00:23:39.230 --> 00:23:40.770
I'll fetch them back right now.

00:23:41.640 --> 00:23:42.210
Don't worry.

00:23:48.100 --> 00:23:50.820
Chongyi, I'll come with you.

00:24:28.310 --> 00:24:29.970
Xiaobangchui, what are you doing at the door?

00:24:29.990 --> 00:24:32.050
Put medicine on my injuries and wrap them.

00:24:59.680 --> 00:25:00.420
Master,

00:25:00.990 --> 00:25:02.820
You must've waited for me so long.

00:25:04.160 --> 00:25:05.730
I finally found you.

00:25:07.160 --> 00:25:07.860
I finally

00:25:09.200 --> 00:25:10.250
Found you.

00:25:55.310 --> 00:25:57.860
Go ahead and cry if you want to.

00:26:04.990 --> 00:26:06.770
Master didn't like seeing me cry.

00:26:11.100 --> 00:26:12.250
I'll hold it in.

00:26:13.710 --> 00:26:15.340
I won't make him fret over me.

00:26:28.510 --> 00:26:29.450
I'll grab some food.

00:27:05.750 --> 00:27:09.730
As the Demon Lord, you'd let a woman order you around.

00:27:20.750 --> 00:27:21.380
My Lord,

00:27:23.960 --> 00:27:27.290
Jiang Lifei is the Divine Tree, right?

00:27:39.680 --> 00:27:41.490
Blame me for being blind

00:27:41.990 --> 00:27:43.580
To her true identity.

00:27:44.920 --> 00:27:45.690
Then again,

00:27:46.550 --> 00:27:48.290
Every Demon Lord ends up falling for the Divine Tree.

00:27:49.100 --> 00:27:51.530
This is our chance to restore the demon clan.

00:27:52.510 --> 00:27:54.900
When are you going to absorb her spirit power?

00:28:05.600 --> 00:28:06.580
Leave her alone.

00:28:08.400 --> 00:28:10.660
Did you forget you're Yecha?

00:28:14.100 --> 00:28:15.140
For hundreds of years,

00:28:16.070 --> 00:28:17.210
No Demon Lord

00:28:17.230 --> 00:28:19.180
Has broken this curse.

00:28:20.340 --> 00:28:21.940
No matter how dedicated

00:28:21.960 --> 00:28:22.900
Or loving you are,

00:28:23.550 --> 00:28:25.210
The Fruit of the Divine Tree

00:28:26.030 --> 00:28:28.010
Will lure you without fail.

00:28:28.790 --> 00:28:30.250
It's just your nature as Yecha.

00:28:31.400 --> 00:28:33.420
If you can't bear to do it yourself,

00:28:35.750 --> 00:28:37.290
I'll handle it for you.

00:28:44.680 --> 00:28:45.250
My Lord,

00:28:46.680 --> 00:28:48.250
Are you really going to kill me?

00:28:58.880 --> 00:29:03.380
After the heaven's wrath, spirit energy grew scarce on the islands,

00:29:04.030 --> 00:29:05.660
And our clansmen could barely survive.

00:29:06.750 --> 00:29:07.820
You promised

00:29:08.640 --> 00:29:12.380
You'd take us back to the Central Plains,

00:29:12.600 --> 00:29:13.620
So we could survive.

00:29:15.470 --> 00:29:17.940
Five centuries ago, after you disappeared,

00:29:18.640 --> 00:29:20.940
The immortal sects hunted our clansmen down.

00:29:21.270 --> 00:29:22.900
We were almost wiped out.

00:29:24.070 --> 00:29:26.420
My Lord, only by absorbing the Divine Tree's power

00:29:27.600 --> 00:29:29.210
Can you gain your Yecha power

00:29:30.030 --> 00:29:32.050
And find our clansmen a way out.

00:29:33.550 --> 00:29:37.380
I live only for you and our clansmen,

00:29:38.070 --> 00:29:39.290
At all costs, without regret.

00:29:39.790 --> 00:29:42.250
But snap out of it, My Lord.

00:29:42.680 --> 00:29:44.970
Save our dying clansmen.

00:30:02.160 --> 00:30:02.690
My Lord.

00:30:05.510 --> 00:30:06.620
You're badly hurt.

00:30:06.960 --> 00:30:08.860
If you don't absorb the Divine Tree's power, your soul will split apart,

00:30:08.880 --> 00:30:09.770
And you'll die in terrible pain.

00:30:09.790 --> 00:30:10.970
I know my own fate!

00:30:14.920 --> 00:30:16.180
If you touch her even once,

00:30:17.750 --> 00:30:19.250
No matter what you've done for me,

00:30:19.960 --> 00:30:21.010
I'll kill you.

00:30:21.120 --> 00:30:22.860
I've always been ready to die

00:30:22.880 --> 00:30:24.770
For you at all times. But what about her?

00:30:25.400 --> 00:30:27.340
Are you going to abandon all of us

00:30:27.360 --> 00:30:28.450
And risk your life for her?

00:30:29.360 --> 00:30:30.380
I'm Lei Xiuyuan.

00:30:32.160 --> 00:30:35.690
Nothing will ever change that.

00:30:43.640 --> 00:30:44.140
My Lord.

00:30:47.840 --> 00:30:50.900
My Lord, don't blame me.

00:30:53.640 --> 00:30:55.580
All is for our clan's future.

00:31:15.750 --> 00:31:18.140
Lifei, eat something.

00:31:20.070 --> 00:31:20.770
I'm okay.

00:31:22.920 --> 00:31:23.690
I wished to burn

00:31:23.710 --> 00:31:25.730
Fine robes for Master,

00:31:27.200 --> 00:31:28.180
Yet all are ragged.

00:31:33.600 --> 00:31:35.050
His final robes were tattered

00:31:37.200 --> 00:31:38.580
Beyond recognition.

00:31:57.270 --> 00:31:57.860
Lifei,

00:32:01.160 --> 00:32:01.940
That strap.

00:32:10.880 --> 00:32:12.290
Master left it for me.

00:32:13.920 --> 00:32:15.250
There must be a story behind it.

00:32:37.550 --> 00:32:38.900
Why's there nothing on it?

00:32:41.070 --> 00:32:44.180
Master, what did you want me to know?

00:32:47.270 --> 00:32:48.290
Xiuyuan, check this with me.

00:32:54.680 --> 00:32:55.290
Xiuyuan!

00:32:55.640 --> 00:32:57.860
Come out! We saw you.

00:32:58.960 --> 00:33:00.180
You have no place to run.

00:33:01.160 --> 00:33:03.530
Guangwei and I are here for you two.

00:33:04.070 --> 00:33:05.210
Only he and I,

00:33:06.600 --> 00:33:08.210
But you can't get away.

00:33:09.880 --> 00:33:12.690
Wait, this place reeks of heavy toxic mist.

00:33:13.070 --> 00:33:14.660
Nobody could stay here.

00:33:16.840 --> 00:33:18.210
That way, go.

00:33:25.510 --> 00:33:27.450
This place is even worse.

00:33:27.600 --> 00:33:28.900
Let's go back there.

00:33:29.270 --> 00:33:31.450
Which path? We've wandered all night.

00:33:31.710 --> 00:33:33.290
You've been looping around, huh?

00:33:34.030 --> 00:33:35.820
Guangwei, don't lose your temper.

00:33:36.030 --> 00:33:37.690
Calm down. Here is the case.

00:33:37.710 --> 00:33:40.290
Look, Qingqiu is huge,

00:33:40.310 --> 00:33:41.940
Plus this heavy toxic fog.

00:33:41.960 --> 00:33:43.420
It messes up our spirit energy,

00:33:43.640 --> 00:33:46.050
So it's normal to get lost.

00:33:46.070 --> 00:33:47.340
Are you here to track them,

00:33:47.680 --> 00:33:48.970
Or sneak them a warning?

00:33:48.990 --> 00:33:49.970
What are you saying?

00:33:49.990 --> 00:33:51.730
I'm obviously here to track them.

00:33:51.880 --> 00:33:53.290
Never mind, I'll look by myself.

00:33:55.510 --> 00:33:57.860
Alright, you lead.

00:33:59.070 --> 00:34:01.340
Watch out. Don't fall into the ditch.

00:34:09.160 --> 00:34:10.620
Xiuyuan, hang in there.

00:34:13.880 --> 00:34:15.300
The Ganhua Realm saved you last time.

00:34:16.070 --> 00:34:17.170
It'll help you again.

00:34:34.440 --> 00:34:35.970
No matter how dedicated

00:34:35.990 --> 00:34:37.050
Or loving you are,

00:34:37.630 --> 00:34:39.220
You'll absorb the Divine Tree's power.

00:34:43.190 --> 00:34:45.420
What's wrong? Feeling sick?

00:34:48.670 --> 00:34:49.260
Xiuyuan.

00:34:49.440 --> 00:34:50.900
I'm okay. Don't come close.

00:34:58.720 --> 00:35:01.220
Is your injury hurting? Let me check.

00:35:01.510 --> 00:35:02.380
Stay away from me.

00:35:11.110 --> 00:35:14.300
Lei Xiuyuan, are you crazy?

00:35:15.460 --> 00:35:16.740
You never mentioned your bad injuries.

00:35:17.070 --> 00:35:18.380
Now you're pushing me away.

00:35:22.420 --> 00:35:23.700
If something bad happens to you...

00:35:28.340 --> 00:35:29.170
Listen up,

00:35:30.780 --> 00:35:33.570
I'd rather die than let you die.

00:35:38.420 --> 00:35:39.490
All of you

00:35:40.940 --> 00:35:41.860
Must live.

00:35:42.820 --> 00:35:43.650
No one's dying!

00:35:47.550 --> 00:35:48.260
Lifei.

00:35:49.820 --> 00:35:53.510
♪The warmth within my arms♪

00:35:53.890 --> 00:35:56.930
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

